text.section:
Upon written notification to the office a purchaser may amend the prepaid tuition contract to change:
The qualified beneficiary, in accordance with 26 U.S.C. sec. 529;
The projected college entrance year for which prepaid tuition is purchased. Beginning July 15, 2014, if the amendment extends the projected college entrance year, the utilization period shall begin with the initial projected college entrance year;
A tuition plan designation to another tuition plan designation;
The number of years for which prepaid tuition is purchased; or
Other provisions of the prepaid tuition contract as permitted by the board.
